Memory Game Documentation
=========================
Language:
    Typescript,
    HTML, and CSS,
    TailwindCss
=========================
Functions:
    Validate():
        Job: Computes the value of two arrays and check for similarities in their values
        Effect: 
            i. Style each box div element to either red or green based on the similarities result.
            ii. Increase the score on a positive similarity result.
=================
NB:
I used a IIFE(Immediately Invoked Function Expression) because I was having |
a problem to get Typescript to work normally.



